---
layout: layouts/docs.njk
title: "Attribute Index"
description: "Complete listing of all attributes — native HTML attributes and VB data attributes — organized by category."
currentSection: api
currentPath: /docs/attributes/
permalink: /docs/attributes/
---

{% block extraHead %}
<style>
    .attribute-index {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--size-m);
      margin-block-start: var(--size-l);
    }

    .attribute-entry {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--size-2xs);
      padding: var(--size-m);
      background: var(--color-surface);
      border: var(--border-width-thin) solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-s);
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .attribute-entry:hover {
      border-color: var(--color-interactive);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px oklch(0% 0 0 / 0.08);
    }

    .attribute-entry code {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .attribute-entry .description {
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      margin: 0;
    }

    .attribute-badge {
      padding: var(--size-3xs) var(--size-xs);
      border-radius: var(--radius-s);
      font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
      font-weight: 500;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .attribute-badge[data-type="native"] {
      background: oklch(85% 0.15 145);
      color: oklch(30% 0.1 145);
    }

    .attribute-badge[data-type="layout"] {
      background: oklch(85% 0.1 200);
      color: oklch(30% 0.1 200);
    }

    .attribute-badge[data-type="behavior"] {
      background: oklch(85% 0.1 60);
      color: oklch(30% 0.1 60);
    }

    .attribute-badge[data-type="formatting"] {
      background: oklch(85% 0.1 250);
      color: oklch(30% 0.1 250);
    }

    .attribute-badge[data-type="styling"] {
      background: oklch(85% 0.1 330);
      color: oklch(30% 0.1 330);
    }

    .filter-bar {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: var(--size-s);
      margin-block: var(--size-l);
      padding: var(--size-m);
      background: var(--color-surface-raised);
      border-radius: var(--radius-m);
      border: none;
    }

    .filter-chip {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--size-xs);
      padding: var(--size-2xs) var(--size-s);
      border: var(--border-width-thin) solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-full);
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
      user-select: none;
      transition: opacity 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .filter-chip input { position: absolute; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }

    .filter-chip:has(input:not(:checked)) {
      opacity: 0.4;
      border-color: transparent;
    }

    .filter-chip:hover {
      border-color: var(--color-interactive);
    }

    .attribute-search {
      margin-block: var(--size-m);
      inline-size: 100%;
      max-inline-size: 400px;
    }

    .attribute-entry[hidden] { display: none; }
    .section-heading[hidden] { display: none; }
    .category-heading[hidden] { display: none; }

    .section-heading {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      margin-block-start: var(--size-xl);
      padding-block-end: var(--size-xs);
      border-block-end: var(--border-width-medium) solid var(--color-border);
      font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .section-heading a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .section-heading a:hover {
      color: var(--color-interactive);
    }

    .category-heading {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      margin-block-start: var(--size-l);
      padding-block-end: var(--size-xs);
      border-block-end: var(--border-width-thin) solid var(--color-border);
      font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .category-heading:first-of-type {
      margin-block-start: 0;
    }
  </style>
{% endblock %}


<h1>Attribute Index</h1>
  <p class="lead">Complete listing of all attributes — native HTML attributes and VB's <code>data-*</code> enhancers — organized by category.</p>

  <fieldset class="filter-bar" aria-label="Filter attributes">
    <legend class="visually-hidden">Filter by type</legend>
    <label class="filter-chip">
      <input type="checkbox" checked data-filter="all" />
      <span>All <strong>{{ attributeIndex.totalCount }}</strong></span>
    </label>
    <label class="filter-chip" data-type="native">
      <input type="checkbox" checked data-filter="native" />
      <span class="attribute-badge" data-type="native">native</span>
      <span><strong>{{ attributeIndex.nativeCount }}</strong></span>
    </label>
    <label class="filter-chip" data-type="layout">
      <input type="checkbox" checked data-filter="layout" />
      <span class="attribute-badge" data-type="layout">layout</span>
      <span><strong>{{ attributeIndex.layoutCount }}</strong></span>
    </label>
    <label class="filter-chip" data-type="behavior">
      <input type="checkbox" checked data-filter="behavior" />
      <span class="attribute-badge" data-type="behavior">behavior</span>
      <span><strong>{{ attributeIndex.behaviorCount }}</strong></span>
    </label>
    <label class="filter-chip" data-type="formatting">
      <input type="checkbox" checked data-filter="formatting" />
      <span class="attribute-badge" data-type="formatting">formatting</span>
      <span><strong>{{ attributeIndex.formattingCount }}</strong></span>
    </label>
    <label class="filter-chip" data-type="styling">
      <input type="checkbox" checked data-filter="styling" />
      <span class="attribute-badge" data-type="styling">styling</span>
      <span><strong>{{ attributeIndex.stylingCount }}</strong></span>
    </label>
  </fieldset>

  <search>
    <input type="search" class="attribute-search" placeholder="Search attributes…" aria-label="Search attributes" />
  </search>

  <nav class="attribute-index" aria-label="All attributes">
    <h2 class="section-heading"><a href="/docs/attributes/native/">Native Attributes</a></h2>
    {% for key, category in attributeIndex.nativeCategories %}
    <h3 class="category-heading">{{ category.label }}</h3>
    {% for item in category.items %}
    <a href="{{ item.href }}" class="attribute-entry" data-type="{{ item.type }}">
      <code>{{ item.name }}</code>
      <span class="attribute-badge" data-type="{{ item.type }}">{{ item.type }}</span>
      {% if item.pack %}<span class="pack-badge"><icon-wc name="package"></icon-wc>{{ item.pack }}</span>{% endif %}
      <p class="description">{{ item.description }}</p>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
    {% endfor %}

    <h2 class="section-heading"><a href="/docs/attributes/data/">Data Attributes</a></h2>
    {% for key, category in attributeIndex.dataCategories %}
    <h3 class="category-heading">{{ category.label }}</h3>
    {% for item in category.items %}
    <a href="{{ item.href }}" class="attribute-entry" data-type="{{ item.type }}">
      <code>{{ item.name }}</code>
      <span class="attribute-badge" data-type="{{ item.type }}">{{ item.type }}</span>
      {% if item.pack %}<span class="pack-badge"><icon-wc name="package"></icon-wc>{{ item.pack }}</span>{% endif %}
      <p class="description">{{ item.description }}</p>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
    {% endfor %}
  </nav>

<script>
(function() {
  var search = document.querySelector('.attribute-search');
  var allCheck = document.querySelector('[data-filter="all"]');
  var typeChecks = document.querySelectorAll('[data-filter]:not([data-filter="all"])');
  var entries = document.querySelectorAll('.attribute-entry');
  var catHeadings = document.querySelectorAll('.category-heading');
  var secHeadings = document.querySelectorAll('.section-heading');

  function update() {
    var query = (search?.value || '').toLowerCase();
    var activeTypes = new Set();
    typeChecks.forEach(function(cb) { if (cb.checked) activeTypes.add(cb.dataset.filter); });

    if (allCheck) allCheck.checked = activeTypes.size === typeChecks.length;

    entries.forEach(function(entry) {
      var type = entry.dataset.type;
      var name = (entry.querySelector('code')?.textContent || '').toLowerCase();
      entry.hidden = !(activeTypes.has(type) && (!query || name.includes(query)));
    });

    catHeadings.forEach(function(h) {
      var next = h.nextElementSibling;
      var hasVisible = false;
      while (next && !next.classList.contains('category-heading') && !next.classList.contains('section-heading')) {
        if (next.classList.contains('attribute-entry') && !next.hidden) hasVisible = true;
        next = next.nextElementSibling;
      }
      h.hidden = !hasVisible;
    });

    secHeadings.forEach(function(h) {
      var next = h.nextElementSibling;
      var hasVisible = false;
      while (next && !next.classList.contains('section-heading')) {
        if (next.classList.contains('attribute-entry') && !next.hidden) hasVisible = true;
        next = next.nextElementSibling;
      }
      h.hidden = !hasVisible;
    });
  }

  if (allCheck) {
    allCheck.addEventListener('change', function() {
      typeChecks.forEach(function(cb) { cb.checked = allCheck.checked; });
      update();
    });
  }
  typeChecks.forEach(function(cb) { cb.addEventListener('change', update); });
  if (search) search.addEventListener('input', update);
})();
</script>
